Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.52,0:00:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Serika{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how excited they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch your step.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.70,0:00:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.37,0:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go join them.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.79,0:00:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.92,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayane{**-chan}, what should we\nlook at first when we get there?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.21,0:00:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question. I think I'd like\nto go see the sea turtles.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.13,0:00:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't most people start with the fish?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Back me up here, you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the seahorses then.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also weirdly specific...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Does sound like something she'd like.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Just look at this place!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're under the sea! {Under da sea --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, there's sharks over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Careful you don't trip and fall!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This aquarium is so big!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not be able to see everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is it {\i1}that{\i0} big?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.69,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like in addition to the fish tanks,\nthe penguin area, and the dolphin show,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.36,0:02:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they also offer a variety of\nother attractions and shops!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.20,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot. Do we rush through all of them?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, the aquarium isn't gonna run away.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can always come back\nanother time if we have to.
Comment: 10,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ojisan noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're all having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.09,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at it gulping!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's how it breathes?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.59,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But hang on, it's underwater.\nHow {\i1}is{\i0} it breathing?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.89,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish have a special organ that\nlets them absorb oxygen from water.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard of gills, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.61,0:03:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Water goes in through their mouths\nand exits after passing over their gills.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.28,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how fish take in oxygen\nand expel carbon dioxide.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In a sense, they breathe just like we do.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.20,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We may look different on the outside,\nbut inside, we're built the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.62,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're ignoring animals like whales\nthat actually hold their breath underwater.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.21,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't really count.\nWhales are mammals, not fish.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's everyone gone all quiet?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I was just a little surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually said something smart for once.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, rude!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're quite the encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to fish, she really is.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks, you're making me blush.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah! I love jellyfish! {can't swim in the night}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.33,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! The way they glow is so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't shining lights\non them or anything, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.17,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. They glow all on their own!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's curious.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.55,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't glowing in the middle of the ocean\njust make it easier to be eaten?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fancy details aside,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,some of them use light to {\i1}protect{\i0} themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They can even use it as a weapon of sorts.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.44,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go look at\nthe tropical fish next, pretty please?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they have a great selection!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.79,0:05:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at those ones! Don't they look just adorable?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.79,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at how plump they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pretty to look at, but imagine the taste!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree with me, right, Ayane{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um, probably wouldn't think to eat them, myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're so cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But think about it this way, Ayane.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could eat these fish,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd save on food.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.15,0:05:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,T-True...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Shiroko{**-senpai}, not you too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nonomi{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.12,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're cute, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.79,0:05:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also think they look quite tasty!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all chatting about?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.38,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Serika{**-chan}, at this point,\nwhy don't we let {*}him{*Sensei} decide?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide what?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.81,0:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, we have a question about the tropical fish.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They look cute, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,They look tasty, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree with {\i1}me{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.52,Alt,,0,0,0,,You agree with {\i1}me{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.11,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.28,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all of you look much cuter? {He really tried it}{God love him, the poor sap --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no. Just... no.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why people make fun of you, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.66,0:06:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! Let me try that again, please?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That fish looks like an old man! {## https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parupeneus_multifasciatus}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Hoshino{**-senpai}'s spirit animal!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It doesn't match her at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.80,0:06:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to pick a spirit animal for her,\nI'd pick something like a jellyfish.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always so laid-back and squishy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you pick, Nonomi{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to pick one...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a penguin?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think they're quite similar!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how cute they are when they waddle their feet! {TRUE! --ML}{holy}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It just jumped higher than our heads!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.63,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! I think they're gonna jump\neven higher next!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}He{*Sensei} looks like he's having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.22,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, almost like he's a little child!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! They're gonna jump again!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.86,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a show!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Shiroko{**-chan}? {two girls alone in a aquarium................................ what will they do....................... (delusion) --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to talk with me privately?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Is this the part where you reveal\nyour undying love for me?! {Yuri archive real? --ML}{I DIDN"T EVEN READ THIS LINE YET AQUARIUM = YURI --rapid}{aquarium = yuri, them's the rules -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It isn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, bummer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.55,0:08:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, during the show,\nI was thinking...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kinda like a dolphin, Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.39,0:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.47,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the others were talking about\nwhat animal I reminded them of earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.19,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was thinking, you're cute and real sporty.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of like a dolphin, y'know?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What animal does li'l ol' me remind you of?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A whale. {Nah, that's Nonomi and her gold card --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.04,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way. I'm too tiny!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit of a stretch.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're similar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how they can swim while sleeping.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how you can only see a part of them, even up close.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How they're always holding their breath.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.44,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, you said you had been taking a nap,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1450,1900,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}but that wasn't true, was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.37,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel like something has been weighing you down.\nSomething you don't want to share.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.58,0:09:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you however I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.09,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you helped me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.93,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so sweet, Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Hoshino{*Senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, that's exactly why...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wuv you so much! {hoshino was the one that confesed in the end............ hm......... --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you make me so happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so lucky we go to the same school!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you girls are getting along well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan} was just telling me\nhow much she loves me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}, let's go to the feeding area next.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. I wonder what fish they have there.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna buy one?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, I mean,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm a little old for a plushie.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't say that!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this beauty!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we can even bring him back with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you {\i1}did{\i0} buy it, where would you put it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sure {*}Teach{*Sensei} would figure something out.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.03,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}True.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.74,0:10:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Doesn't Hoshino{**-senpai} look\njust adorbs with that huge whale?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.25,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything you like, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this looks nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.47,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a surprisingly normal choice,\ncoming from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But it probably costs a good bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, you don't have to worry about that part.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, we could go for\nsomething smaller, like a keychain...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, right, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I mean... {## this is burning into his gunpla funds!!!}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}? {wiggly wiggly intonation --ik}{Like a jellyfish! --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy you're happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.09,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now that we're all here, let's take a picture!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.76,0:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll take the photo,\nso go line up over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't you joining us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.61,0:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting shy about now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.82,0:11:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're part of the gang now, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave you out of this, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to take it for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuka!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy meeting you here, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.54,0:12:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again for your help last time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been well, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.38,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might take the opportunity\nto discuss something with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.14,0:12:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I'd better save it for another time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.27,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, we can take the photo for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gladly take you up on that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here we go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "cheese"!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These are the kind of moments\nthey deserve to have more of.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope I'm just overthinking it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way I am now...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.21,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I doing a good enough{™️} job{! media},
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yume{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I imagining things?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks gorgeous in profile.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gorgeous normally.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.01,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Should I send this\nin the Momotalk group?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We should all upload the photos we took.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Hoshino{**-senpai},\nshe's not here yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's off napping somewhere again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.11,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you also send over\nthe photos you took yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.33,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, I hadn't sent\nanything besides the group photo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, where did you take this? {iwak --rapid}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a specimen area.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They said we could hold them, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.17,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're posing with the day's catch!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you would be pretty good at fishing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.81,0:15:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I might try it out if we get the chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go to the actual ocean next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.60,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That underwater tunnel was really cool, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go diving or something one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.61,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. If that happens,\nwe should all go together again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, gang. How's it hanging?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.58,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just so comfy in my bed,\nI didn't wanna get out.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's everyone up to?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.80,0:16:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We were looking at the aquarium pictures.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.01,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me in on the fun, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.01,0:16:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you take any, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.14,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At my age, it's hard to keep up\nwith all this fancy schmancy technology.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fancy schmancy"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.85,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure to take plenty of pics\nof both you and everyone else!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going, Nonomi{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.90,0:16:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what I'd like to say, but I knew you'd be\ntoo busy taking pics of everyone else,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so I made sure to take plenty of you as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I also took pictures of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.75,0:17:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}, Ayane{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both so thoughtful! I'm touched!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shiroko{**-chan}. Aren't you going to join them?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I love you two as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.15,0:17:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone,\nthat's it for today's regular meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.78,Alt,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also heading home now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go say bye to {*}Teacher{*Sensei} before I go.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.00,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go home and have a nice snooze.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.26,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you this morning?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't go anywhere.\nI just overslept a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.19,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw you in town this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you had the wrong person.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of girls who look just like me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.79,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you were so tired from yesterday\nyou started seeing things?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take it easy for today and go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.55,0:18:30.46,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hiding something from—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You took pictures of me, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.85,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'll send you the pics\nthe others took as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Owwie...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Hoshino{*Senpai}, what is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a form.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything yet, so relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I can relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "yet"?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.75,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put this...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}? Shiroko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but please leave us alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that's a no.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.19,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no keeping secrets in the Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.07,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all in this together, as a team!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really no big deal, so no worries.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}'s such a worrywart.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.09,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really do appreciate the thought, honest.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.76,0:20:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hoshino{**-senpai}, I'm not done—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened between you two,\nbut maybe you should give her some space.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hoshino{**-senpai}'s—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.40,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has things they'd rather not talk about.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshino...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the time has finally come.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, this is the point of no return.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we move forward with this,\nthere's no going back.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.13,0:22:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.22,0:22:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've calmed down a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.52,0:22:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.02,0:22:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.94,0:23:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.15,0:23:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai} is hiding something from us.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.45,0:23:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.16,0:23:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's that Hoshino doesn't trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.71,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you leave this to me for now?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.59,0:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help her, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.63,0:23:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.80,0:23:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are things she can't tell you\n{\i1}because{\i0} she trusts and cares about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.77,0:23:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.52,0:23:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{=9}Thank you, {*}Teacher{*Sensei}.

